// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2625 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 6a90bd71-6c1a-55dc-a1f0-19d136022812

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
